node.text:
Currently bawling my eyes out because I’ve been waiting over a year for this day to come! 😭🙏
.
I poured SO much love, sweat, tears (& waffle mix 😉) into this cookbook & I am so very proud of what I created.
.
This is more than just a cookbook, though. On top of the 90 delicious, macro-friendly recipes, I also included my fit tips & quick & effective workouts that you can do from anywhere! Including your kitchen, or even your van if you’re like me! 🏠
.
Each recipe uses one simple, compact & not to mention cute, Dash mini waffle maker! If you’ve been here for awhile, you know how much I LOVE this thing!
.
My passion is to help as many people as possible create healthier relationships with food & fitness.
.
That’s why I created a cookbook filled with a wide variety of healthy, easy to make recipes full of amazing flavor, but not all the extra calories.
.
I used to believe that performing & looking my best, meant that I had to eat the same, boring basic foods over & over again. 
.
Then I found out the Dash mini waffle maker, & I discovered that cooking can actually be fun & that it is possible to LOVE food & LOVE my body at the same time! 💛
.
Don’t worry, I also included some treat meals. 😋
.
Recipes are also conveniently portioned to 1 or 2 servings, so it’s great for college students living in a dorm, or frequent travelers/van lifers, like me! It’s perfect for parents because it’s fun for the kids, as well as busy bees because the mini waffle maker heats in just seconds & cooks most of the recipes in this book in just a few minutes! 🙌
.
Get my Waffly Fit Cookbook AND the @bydash mini waffle maker together in a perfectly packaged gift set for JUST $24.99! 😀
.
You can also buy my book by itself for $19.99 🙌
.
Watch the full video for more info & to see the book in action! And visit my website (clairepthomas.com). Click the link in my bio to purchase directly. 🙌
.
Love you all a waffle lot! Thank you so much for your support. 💛🧇 
.
Video edit by @turningtreeproductions
.
#teamcpt #cookbook #healthyfood #healthycooking #waffles #healthywaffles #proteinwaffles #iam1stphorm #fitfood #fitfoodie #health-coac

node.text:
Happy Monday guys! Here’s this week’s #clairecorechallenge + GIVEAWAY! 👊
.
This exercise takes toes to bar to a whole new world! I call it, “around the world T2B.” 🌎😉 The goal it to keep your legs as straight as possible as you bring them up & around the bar. To make things technical, you’ve gotta actually touch your toes to that bar every rep & bring them up & above it. But this is just for fun, so give it your best effort & if your toes don’t make it that far don’t worry about it! I also included a modified version where you keep your knees bent. 😊
.
One lucky person who tries any sort of variation of this exercise will receive a free CPT Fit Guide of choice!
.
All you have to do is film yourself ATTEMPTING (it doesn’t have to look pretty 😆) this exercise, tag me on your story & use the hashtag, #clairecorechallenge 💪 The more bloopers the better. 🤗
.
I do NOT choose the winner based on how well or how many reps. The weekly winner will be selected completely randomly from the pool of people who tag me throughout each week! 🙌
.
So, grab a pull-up bar & give this one a shot! Tag your homies who also need to try for a chance to win one of my training programs. 💪
.
To learn more about all the programs I offer, click the link in my bio for my website!
.
I will announce the winner on my story next week, when I share next week’s new core challenge!
.
GOOD LUCK! 💪
.
Song: “No Sleep” by Martin Garrix
.
.
#teamcpt #coreworkout #fitnesschallenge #fitchallenge #workoutchallenge #abs #absworkout #sixpack #6pack #strongcore #iamstphorm #personaltrainer #challengeyourself #giveawaycontest #giveaway

node.text:
Hopped islands & hit a giant reset button this weekend. 🌊
.
In between goals is a thing called life, that has to be loved & enjoyed...
.
I needed this.
Less time looking at my laptop.
More time looking into eyes.
Less minutes immersed in stress.
More minutes immersed in nature.
.
If you’re a workaholic, like me, this is my reminder to you to TAKE A DANG BREAK from time to time.
.
I’m quite literally addicted to my job. My business is my baby & I wouldn’t trade it for the world.
.
It doesn’t matter how much you love what you or how passionate you are, it is SO important to unplug every now & then otherwise you’ll burn out.
.
I’ve learned this the hard way & I’m sure many of you can relate.
.
Here are some ways I recharge when I feel my battery running on reserve:👇
.
1) Put all my devices away.
2) Hug someone.
3)Get lost in nature or go on a walk outside.
4) Put something funny on TV & laugh out loud.
5) Drive down backroads & sing my favorite songs at the top of my lungs.
6) Call an old friend.
7) Deep clean the house/van.
8) Find an amazing place to watch the sunrise/sunset
9) Date night at your favorite restaurant
10)Buy a last minute plane ticket
.
Guys, can you  believe it’s already August!? I encourage you all to do what you need to today to take care of yourself - to reset & recharge - so that when you wake up tomorrow morning you’re ready & motivated to make the most of this new month of new potential & possibilities. 💛
.
Please comment below a couple things you do to recharge &/or if we have any in common. 🙌
.
Love you all so big. 💛
.
.
.
#teamcpt #kauaihawaii #rechargeyoursoul #recharge #resetbutton #islandhopping #takeabreak #kauai #hilife #personaltrainer #healthcoach #balanceiskey #iam1stphorm

node.text:
f r i d a y  f e e l i n ☀️
.
Jk, I’m never really “off duty.” But that’s exactly how I like it. I LOVE what I do.
.
Which Friday mood are you? 1 or 2? 😆
.
I hope you take a moment today, & everyday, to understand the value you hold. You are here for a reason. You are important & you are loved. Have a great weekend friends. ☺️
.
#teamcpt #fridayfeeling #fridaymood #mauihawaii

node.text:
Throwback to this fun workout I forgot to share from my Power Partner Guide! 👯‍♀️💪
.
Did you know that you are 2X more likely to stick to your fitness regimen with a partner?! 🤗 It doesn’t matter if it’s your significant other, your best friend, your co-worker, your mom, your brother or someone else. Find that someone who can hold you accountable & push you to your limits!
.
My Power Partner Guide is an 8-week training program full of fun yet challenging partner workouts that you & your buddy can do from home (or anywhere) because most workouts only require your bodyweight! 💪
.
Each exercise is linked to a video tutorial demonstrating proper form & technique. I also included low & high intensity cardio workouts, core workouts, my top nutrition & fit tips, a complete warm-up & cool-down & SO much more! 🙌
.
For more info, click the link in my bio or go to www.clairepthomas.com
.
👉Swipe to the end & screenshot the workout taken directly from my Power Partner Guide!
.
Tag your workout partner in crime & get to work! 👊👯‍♀️
.
Mine was my amazing, talented & sweet friend @char.hendrix 💛
.
.
.
#teamcpt #partnerworkout #workoutpartner #trainingpartner #workoutbuddy #teamworkout #workoutmotivation #iam1stphorm #wedothework #funworkout #workoutwithfriends #partnerwod

node.text:
My chicas, stop skipping chest day! Here’s why…
.
Our bodies work as a beautiful & powerful unit. It is very important to not ignore any muscle group so that we can work as efficiently as possible.
.
There’s this misconception out there that chest workouts will make your breasts smaller, which many women fear. Now, I know I’m not a great example as I am a proud member of the itty bitty titty committee 🤣, but here’s the truth: Boobs are made up of fatty tissue & you cannot simply spot reduce fat. Therefore, bench pressing will NOT shrink your tatas. However, if you train & eat in a way that is conducive to weight loss, you will lose fat throughout your body, which inevitably leads to a smaller belly, arms, & yes, even boobs.
.
If your workout routine consists of training all other muscles while neglecting your chest, this off-balance training routine could end up creating bad posture & muscular imbalances in your body, further leading to the inability to perform other exercises correctly, even daily tasks & activities like pushing a stroller, opening/closing a heavy door, or throwing a ball.
.
Lifting your chest has other perks, too. Pun 100% intended. 😉 Building the pectorals will in fact make the ladies perkier & more well rounded. 🙌
.
For anyone who’s guilty of skipping chest day, I hope this convinced you to break that habit & to get after it with this chest & triceps workout. 💪
.
D E E T S :
.
SUPERSET x 3 ROUNDS:
1️⃣ EZ BAR NARROW CHEST PRESS
🔆 15 reps
2️⃣ EX BAR SKULL CRUSHERS
🔆 15 reps
REST 60 SECS
.
3️⃣ BENCH PRESS
🔆 5 sets | 5 reps (build weight each set)
Rest as needed
.
4️⃣ CHEST FLY
🔆 3 sets | 10 reps (build weight each set)
Rest as needed
.
CIRCUIT x 3 ROUNDS:
5️⃣ LYING PLATE SQUEEZE PRESSES
🔆 12 reps
6️⃣ DIPS
🔆 12 reps
7️⃣ DECLINE PUSH UPS
🔆 12 reps
REST 60 SECS
.
SUPERSET x 3 ROUNDS:
7️⃣ RACKED BB INCINE WIDE PUSH UPS
🔆 10 reps
8️⃣ RACKED BB TRICEP EXTENSIONS
🔆 10 reps
REST 60 SECS
.
Your turn. 👊
.
PS: my Work Hard & Be Nice to People tanks are back in stock!! Link in bio 💛
.

node.text:
w a f f l e s  by the  w a v e s 🧇🌊 
.
You guys gotta try my peanut butter banana nut protein waffles! They are so tasty & you’d never guess that they are good for you, too! 😋
.
D E E T S :
.
Serves ✌️
.
For batter:
.
•1 cup PB Kodiak Cakes mix OR regular waffle mix & 2 Tbsp powdered PB
•1 scoop Chocolate Banana Level-1 protein (link in bio for my supps)
•2/3 cup almond milk

For on top:
.
•Sliced banana
•Protein nut butter
•Whipped cream
•Sugar free syrup
.
Directions:
.
1️⃣ Combine all batter ingredients in a bowl & mix until smooth.
2️⃣ Plug in waffle maker & spray with non-stick cooking spray.
3️⃣ Pour spoonfuls of batter inside & cook until crispy. Repeat until all better is cooked. If using a mini waffle maker, 3 Tbsp batter makes one waffle & it takes about 99 seconds to cook each waffle.
4️⃣ Place 3 waffles on 2 plates & add toppings.
5️⃣ Enjoy! 😋
.
Last November I launched my Waffly Fit Cookbook. Now, this isn’t your average cookbook. Each recipe uses one simple, compact & not to mention CUTE, mini waffle maker! It you’ve been here for awhile, you know how much I LOVE this thing!
.
I included over 90 delicious & nutritious recipes & they’re not all waffles! I’m talkin pizza, tacos, sandwiches, wraps, brownies, cinnamon rolls & so much more! 😋
.
As a health & fitness coach, my passion is to help as many people as possible create healthier relationships with food & fitness.
.
I wanted to create a cookbook filled with a wide variety of healthy, easy to make recipes full of amazing flavor, but not all the extra calories & crap!
.
What makes this book truly unique, Is that I also included my fit tips & quick & effective workouts that you can do from anywhere! Including your kitchen, or even your van if you’re like me! 🏠🚐
.
Check it out on my website or click the link in my bio! 🧇😊
.
.
.
#teamcpt #teamwaffles #vanlife #vanlifetheworld #sprintervan #mauihawaii #waffles #healthyrecipe #proteinwaffles #fitfood #fuelyourbody #fuelgood #wafflyfitcookbook #iamstphorm #healthcoach

node.text:
It’s that time again! Announcing this week’s #clairecorechallenge + GIVEAWAY! 👊
.
Happy Sunday beautiful people!☺️ This was a fun one & WAY more challenging than I thought it would be!
.
Every weekend I share a weekly core challenge & one lucky person who tries it will receive a free CPT Fit Guide of choice!
.
All you have to do is film yourself or a friend ATTEMPTING (it doesn’t have to look pretty 😆) this exercise, tag me on your story & use the hashtag, #clairecorechallenge 💪 The more bloopers the better. 🤗
.
I do NOT choose the winner based on how well or how many reps. The weekly winner will be selected completely randomly from the pool of people who tag me throughout each week! 🙌
.
So, grab a medicine ball (mine weighed 12 pounds) & give this workout a shot! Tag your homies who also need to try for a chance to win one of my training programs. 💪
.
To learn more about all the programs I offer, click the link in my bio for my website!
.
I will announce the winner on my story next weekend, when I share next week’s new core challenge!
.
GOOD LUCK! 💪
.
.
.
#teamcpt #coreworkout #fitnesschallenge #workoutchallenge #abs #absworkout #sixpack #6pack #strongcore #iamstphorm #personaltrainer

node.text:
Happy Friday Friends. 🤗 Here’s a fast, fun, full body finisher for your next workout! 👊🔥
.
Do you ever finish a workout & feel like you have more gas left in the tank? Do you ever walk out of the gym regretting not pushing a little harder? How about, do you ever simply just want to sweat more, torch more calories & leave the gym feeling accomplished as heck?! MEEEE 🙋🏼‍♀️
.
These are the reasons I love adding quick, high intensity finishers like this to the end of my workouts every so often, if I know I have more left in me. 💪
.
How fast can you crush this one?!
.
D E E T S :
.
4 rounds of the following 3 exercises, as fast as you possibly can! 👇
.
1️⃣ TOES TO BAR OR LYING LEG RAISES
🔥 20 REPS
2️⃣ THRUSTERS
🔥 15 REPS (I used 30lb DBs)
3️⃣ SPRINT
🔥 400 METERS
.
Get after it & tag your training partner who should, too! 💪
.
Song: Fading Memories by Adon, Nicolas Haegl & Sam Halabi
.
.
.
#teamcpt #fullbodyworkout #workoutmotivation #workoutoftheday #wodoftheday #t2b #coreworkout #hiitworkout #hiit #hiitworkouts #personaltrainer #onlinefitnesscoach #iam1stphorm

node.text:
It don’t matter to me, wherever we are is where I want to be.
.
And Honey, for once in our lives
let’s take our chances & roll the dice.
.
I can be your lucky penny.
.
You can be my four-leaf clover.
.
Starting over.
.
Now this might not be an easy time.
There’s rivers to cross & hills to climb.
.
Some days we might fall apart
And some nights might feel cold & dark.
.
But nobody wins afraid of losing
& the hard roads are the ones worth choosing.
.
Some days we’ll look back & smile
And know it was worth every mile.
.
@chrisstapleton , did you write this song for us?? Because it kinda feels like you did. ☺️
.
I love it almost as much as I love this guy @jaredconnell
.
💛🚐👩🏼‍🤝‍👨🏻

node.text:
Spicy leg day comin your way! 🔥
.
Boy did this one hurt! But that’s the point, right?! If your workouts don’t make you uncomfortable or challenged, you’re doin them wrong. Nothing worth having comes easy. Intensity is CRUCIAL if you want to see the best results from your training. 💪
.
It’s not about the amount of weight. It’s about your amount of effort.
.
It’s not about how long your workout is. It’s about how effectively you use your time.
.
A little tip that has helped me is getting in the habit of asking myself throughout my workouts if I’m giving it everything I’ve got. Can I push a just a little harder or move a little faster? Can I go for 1 more rep or increase my weight by 5 more pounds? The answer is always yes... and I then I just do it. Those little mental cues & reminders could get you the results you’re looking for a whole lot sooner & make you feel way more proud & accomplished at the end of your workout. 🙌
.
D E E T S :
.
PART 1 - 20 minute AMRAP - complete as many rounds as possible of the following 3 exercises. Rest as needed.
.
1️⃣ WALKING OVERHEAD BARBELL LUNGES
🔥 10 reps each leg
2️⃣ BROAD JUMPS
🔥 10 reps
3️⃣ GOBLET SQUAT
🔥 10 reps
.
Rest 5 minutes, then complete:
.
PART 2 -
.
4️⃣ BULGARIAN SPLIT SQUATS
🔥 3 sets x 8 reps each leg
THEN 👉 Find your 3 rep (both legs) max. Add weight each set until you can’t add any more. I got up to 185 for 3 each leg. 😵
.
Your turn! 👊 Save for your next leg day!
.
.
.
#teamcpt #legday #legworkout #bulgariansplitsquats #mauihawaii #squats #personaltrainer #duespaid #fitnesscoach #iam1stphorm

node.text:
Back & biceps babyyyy!! 💪🔥
.
Woof this one was fire!! I had some fun with the cable machine & tried a couple new exercise variations to mix things up!
.
If you enjoy supersets, you’ll love my CPT Fit Guide 2.0. The whole 8 week training program revolves around supersets. 🙌
.
A superset is when you alternate between two exercises for one combined set with minimal rest in between. I honestly get a little bored lifting if I don’t do my exercises in a superset or in a circuit. 😅 Not only that, but supersets make your workouts faster & feel more intense! 👊
.
I’m currently alternating between bodybuilding style workouts like this one, CrossFit & bodyweight workouts.
.
If you’re interested in following a training program for any or all of these training styles, I’ve got you covered! Check out the Fit Guides I offer & personally use myself at clairepthomas.com or click the link in my bio. 💪
.
WORKOUT DEETS:
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ LYING CABLE CURLS
💥 10 reps
2️⃣ SEATED CABLE ROWS
💥 10 reps
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ DB CROSS BODY HAMMER CURLS
💥 10 reps each arm
2️⃣ NARROW GRIP PULL DOWN
💥10 reps
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ DB CURL 21’S
💥 7 low, 7 high, 7 full
2️⃣ STRAIGHT ARM STANDING HIGH ROW + STRAIGHT ARM PULL DOWN
💥 5 reps each way, each arm
.
🔆SUPERSET - 3 rounds of the following 2 exercises. Rest 1-2 mins, only between rounds:
1️⃣ CHIN UPS
💥 8-10 reps
2️⃣ PULL UPS
💥 8-10 reps
.
Happy Monday Fam! 💛
.
Tag your workout partner in crime who needs to get after this one & save it for your next back & biceps workout. 💪
.
.
.
#teamcpt #backworkout #backattack #backday #backandbiceps #pullups #iam1stphorm #workoutmotivation #mauihawaii #wedothework #personaltrainer #fitnesscoach

node.text:
It’s another crazy core workout challenge + GIVEAWAY! 👊🔥
.
Happy Sunday Homies! ☺️
.
Every weekend I’ll be sharing a weekly core challenge & one lucky person who tries it will receive a free CPT Fit Guide of choice!
.
D E E T S 👇
.
Complete 2-3 rounds of the following exercises:
.
1️⃣ PLATE LEG RAISES
🔥 8 reps
.
2️⃣ PLATE KNEE RAISE HOLD + KNEE RAISE HOLD
🔥 Hold until failure, drop weight
& hold until failure without weight
.
3️⃣ PLATE SIT UPS
🔥 12 reps
.
4️⃣ PLATE RUSSIAN TWISTS
🔥 12 reps each side
.
5️⃣ PLATE STANDING SIDE DIPS
🔥 12 reps each side
.
To enter the giveaway, all you have to do is film yourself or a friend attempting an exercise from this workout, tag me on your story & use the hashtag, #clairecorechallenge 💪
.
I’m NOT choosing the winners based on how well or how many reps. The weekly winner will be selected completely randomly from the pool of people who tag me throughout each week! 🙌
.
So, grab a weight plate & give this workout a shot! Tag someone who also needs to try for a chance to win one of my training programs. 💪
.
To learn more about all the programs I offer, click the link in my bio for my website!
.
I will announce the winner on my story next weekend, when I share next week’s new core challenge!
.
GOOD LUCK! 💪
.
.
.
#teamcpt #corechallenge #abs #absworkout #sixpack #sixpackabs #6packabs #corechallenge #fitnesschallenge #giveaway #strongcore #workoutmotivation #iam1stphorm #mauihawaii
